{"tid":1511694,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇咗民調咁耐 課咗金未？","createTime":"2019-08-27T15:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:12:05.000Z","uid":34515,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4264a26365728ec6730de06a4a35c50609ec05","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"香港人嘢自己撐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我頭先申請order no先500幾<br />\n如果我真係第500幾位做會員定期課金<br />\n我諗佢每個月收到嘅數真係唔夠support做長期民調<br />\n<br />\n其實收集同處理數據唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得有個可信 有質素 公正嘅民調機構研究下社會輿論<br />\n大家應該多啲支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗林鄭民望 仲有好多政府高官 北京信任度<br />\n一國兩制 對中國/香港前途信心 民生 企業等嘅研究<br />\n好有參考價值㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似好hard sell<br />\n但真實數據對我哋運動其實好有用<br />\n例如我哋知道到林鄭民望低處未算低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算係反映民意冇因爲運動升級而有好大反彈<br />\n仲可以寫落歷史 用數據證明宜家社會有幾不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iguzMJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiguzMJa.png&h=e5f54996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身諗住俾多啲<br />\n但要買糧票俾可愛又勇敢義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8.28 1點國泰城 8點遮打見<br />\n8.31 民陣遊行見<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d5d4f9b678ef64c16f7252a308ff54386edafb8a","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"76c6569bd17f0c16eb020ef25eef5ab075c92dad","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"8852b19d004b431ec10ee718adf819d996dcef7a","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"3a82ae692ddef6440475b86963cd050fbcda1dd7","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"033808bfe5dfd265b4138bcfade8ef67ce8ad509","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"62ccc6f2490b5fc2fb91907c87689c67542ad893","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"c36eec8c567a4b19e660e1455bbc8be57ac2a128","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"推7/10"},{"pid":"7a9125be3bb537232391ea40fb6560d04fc735db","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"推8/10"},{"pid":"7108702bee8dbb31be9743bd3e918619fec1d5cb","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"推9/10"},{"pid":"06761fad470e00ec72b5d749e0652e25fe7f36a4","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"推10/10"},{"pid":"b6ad1216a3dfa131d22ce8bd16f8a90c3a78aac9","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2c0b0818b96257c3feafedd244298bfd92961b","tid":1511694,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd10b55c5dc58008436d4480618a2aaa09531aa","tid":1511694,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":